_sText:
JAIL BREAK

jb_underground is finally here with version 1! Been working on this project for months now off and on. Finally buckled down and completed as much as I wanted to. A map is never really finished.
Map is about 80-90% optimized. It could be optimized more but I don't know much about it. It's my first real map after all. My other two projects were really just learning experiences. 
The map features games that terrorist can play (with a willing warden) 
Those games are:
Simon says (colors)
Pick-a-color (new concept by me)
81 square break floor
volleyball
ice race (climb)
death crate

It also features 
Secrets
Medic
Disco
Pool
A pit (isolation)
A secret lambda room that acts as a bomb site that to gain access to you must find 3 secret buttons located throughout the level. Goodluck. (note: if a T drops the bomb the bomb disappears)

Special thanks to GP's own OhhDandy for his medic prefab.
